data.description:
Oro Valley - (La Canada/Moore Rd)  2145 sq.ft. 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, Formal Living Area, Family Room and Separate Dinning Area, All Stainless Steel Appliances, Electric Cooking and Heating, Master Suite w/ Walk in Closet, Double Sink in Master Bath w/Garden Tub and Separate Shower, Tile & Carpet Through out, Laundry Room w/Washer, Dryer and Sink, 2 car garage, Mature Landscaping in Front Yard on Drip Irrigation System . Please call office to schedule an appointment 520-297-5593.
Contact us to schedule a showing.
